query:
UPDATE initiatives 
SET priorityQuadrant = CASE
  WHEN effortScore <= 5 AND returnScore > 5 THEN 'quick-win'
  WHEN effortScore > 5 AND returnScore > 5 THEN 'strategic-bet'
  WHEN effortScore <= 5 AND returnScore <= 5 THEN 'nice-to-have'
  WHEN effortScore > 5 AND returnScore <= 5 THEN 'reconsider'
  ELSE NULL
END
WHERE effortScore IS NOT NULL AND returnScore IS NOT NULL;
